---
import Layout from "@/layouts/Layout.astro";
import Container from "@/components/container.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="Press Mentions & Media Coverage"
  description="Comprehensive media coverage of the 12-year journey from Startup Village to EduMyna"
>
  <Container>
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto py-16 md:py-24">
      <!-- Hero Section -->
      <div class="mb-16">
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">Press Mentions & Media Coverage</h1>
        <p class="text-lg text-slate-600 mb-6">
          Chronological collection of media stories documenting the 12-year journey from Startup Village (2009) to SV.CO, Pupilfirst, and beyond.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
          <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-blue-50 text-blue-700 text-sm font-medium rounded-full">BBC Coverage</span>
          <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-blue-50 text-blue-700 text-sm font-medium rounded-full">#1 Incubator Ranking</span>
          <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-blue-50 text-blue-700 text-sm font-medium rounded-full">30+ Media Stories</span>
          <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-blue-50 text-blue-700 text-sm font-medium rounded-full">2013-2019</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- 2013: BBC Coverage -->
      <div class="mb-12">
        <p class="text-xs font-bold tracking-wider uppercase text-slate-400 mb-2">2012-2014 - Startup Village Era</p>
        <div class="space-y-3">
          <div class="bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-lg p-4">
            <a href="https://www.bbc.com/news/business-22205601" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-base font-semibold text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-700">BBC Business - India's 'Silicon Coast' ↗</a>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 mt-1">BBC coverage of Startup Village as India's first PPP incubator building Kerala's "Silicon Coast"</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-lg p-4">
            <a href="https://www.bbc.com/news/av/business-22210389" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-base font-semibold text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-700">BBC Video - Startup Village Feature ↗</a>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 mt-1">BBC video coverage of the physical incubator and student entrepreneurship programs</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-lg p-4">
            <p class="text-base font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-1">A Company that Mentors Young Entrepreneurs | A 'school' for startups</p>
            <div class="flex gap-3 mt-2">
              <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LCsQ68plQos" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-sm text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-700">YouTube ↗</a>
              <a href="https://www.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=1234205526639360&id=417921431601111&_rdr" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-sm text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-700">Facebook ↗</a>
            </div>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 mt-2">Documentary-style feature on Startup Village's mentorship model</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-lg p-4">
            <a href="https://www.siliconindia.com/shownews/www.siliconindia.com/shownews/indias-first-startup-village-at-kochi-nid-103361-cid-100.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-base font-semibold text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-700">Silicon India - India's First Startup Village at Kochi ↗</a>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 mt-1">Tech industry coverage of India's pioneering PPP incubator model</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-lg p-4">
            <a href="https://www.thenewsminute.com/news/kochi-startup-village-countrys-best-46936" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-base font-semibold text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-700">The News Minute - Kochi Startup Village: Country's Best ↗</a>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 mt-1">Regional news coverage of Startup Village's achievements and impact</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-lg p-4">
            <a href="https://www.indiascienceandtechnology.gov.in/innovations/incubators/startup-village-kochi" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-base font-semibold text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-700">India Science & Technology Portal - Startup Village ↗</a>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 mt-1">Official Government of India portal listing Startup Village as a key incubator</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-lg p-4">
            <a href="https://www.crunchbase.com/organization/startup-village" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-base font-semibold text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-700">Crunchbase - Startup Village Profile ↗</a>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 mt-1">Company profile with timeline, funding info, and key milestones</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-lg p-4">
            <a href="https://medium.com/@undead555/my-experiences-with-startup-village-df2f7d5cb9e9" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-base font-semibold text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-700">Medium - My Experiences with Startup Village ↗</a>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 mt-1">First-hand account from a participant's perspective</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- 2016: #1 Incubator Ranking -->
      <div class="mb-12">
        <p class="text-xs font-bold tracking-wider uppercase text-slate-400 mb-2">2016 - Ranked #1 Incubator in India</p>
        <div class="space-y-3">
          <div class="bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-lg p-4">
            <a href="https://www.financialexpress.com/industry/kochi-startup-village-countrys-best/325625/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-base font-semibold text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-700">Financial Express - Kochi Startup Village: Country's Best ↗</a>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 mt-1">Coverage of Startup Village being ranked #1 incubator in India</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-lg p-4">
            <a href="https://www.business-standard.com/article/pti-stories/kerala-s-startup-village-ranked-india-s-best-incubator-116072201221_1.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-base font-semibold text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-700">Business Standard - India's Best Incubator ↗</a>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 mt-1">Business Standard coverage of the #1 ranking achievement</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-lg p-4">
            <a href="https://blog.sv.co/startup-village-ranked-1-amongst-indian-incubators-b78b5b281572" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-base font-semibold text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-700">SV.CO Blog - Ranked #1 Announcement ↗</a>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 mt-1">Official announcement and reflection on achieving #1 incubator status</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- 2016: Going Digital -->
      <div class="mb-12">
        <p class="text-xs font-bold tracking-wider uppercase text-slate-400 mb-2">2016 - Digital Transformation</p>
        <div class="space-y-3">
          <div class="bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-lg p-4">
            <p class="text-base font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-1">Economic Times - Startup Village COO talks about going completely digital</p>
            <div class="flex gap-3 mt-2 flex-wrap">
              <a href="https://economictimes.indiatimes.com/et-now/tech/startup-village-coo-talks-about-going-completely-digital/videoshow/53161490.cms" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-sm text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-700">ET Article ↗</a>
              <a href="https://youtu.be/2mfgd6LjWNA" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-sm text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-700">YouTube (User) ↗</a>
              <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=H1kClGNav-0" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-sm text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-700">YouTube (Alt) ↗</a>
              <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=k_0fF0jTb1Y" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-sm text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-700">YouTube (Original) ↗</a>
            </div>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 mt-2">Interview about the strategic pivot from physical incubator to digital-first platform</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- SV.CO Medium Blog -->
      <div class="mb-12 bg-blue-50 border-2 border-blue-200 rounded-xl p-6">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-blue-600 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
            <span class="text-white font-bold text-xl">M</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="text-lg font-bold text-blue-900">SV.CO Medium Blog</p>
            <a href="https://medium.com/@SVdotCO" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-sm text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-700">@SVdotCO ↗</a>
            <span class="mx-2 text-slate-400">·</span>
            <a href="https://medium.com/sv-co-blog" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-sm text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-700">medium.com/sv-co-blog ↗</a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-700 mb-4">First-hand accounts, stories, and updates from the SV.CO team (2016-2018)</p>

        <div class="space-y-3">
          <div class="bg-white border border-blue-200 rounded-lg p-4">
            <a href="https://medium.com/sv-co-blog/about" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-base font-semibold text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-700">About SV.CO ↗</a>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 mt-1">Overview of SV.CO's mission and vision for digital student entrepreneurship</p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white border border-blue-200 rounded-lg p-4">
            <a href="https://medium.com/sv-co-blog/scaling-startup-village-the-sv-co-story-b5d033ccbdd1" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-base font-semibold text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-700">Scaling Startup Village: The SV.CO Story! (April 2016) ↗</a>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 mt-1">How Startup Village pivoted from physical to digital incubation</p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white border border-blue-200 rounded-lg p-4">
            <a href="https://medium.com/sv-co-blog/startup-village-ranked-1-amongst-indian-incubators-b78b5b281572" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-base font-semibold text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-700">Startup Village ranked #1 amongst Indian Incubators (July 2016) ↗</a>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 mt-1">Celebrating the #1 ranking and what it meant for the team</p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white border border-blue-200 rounded-lg p-4">
            <a href="https://medium.com/sv-co-blog/manipal-university-students-adopt-entrepreneurship-as-a-way-of-life-e0c5f5a676e5" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-base font-semibold text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-700">Manipal University students adopt entrepreneurship as a way of life (May 2017) ↗</a>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 mt-1">Student story from the university partnership program</p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white border border-blue-200 rounded-lg p-4">
            <a href="https://medium.com/sv-co-blog/learning-startup-basics-with-sv-co-d781dbe8409d" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-base font-semibold text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-700">Learning startup basics with SV.CO (October 2017) ↗</a>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 mt-1">A founder's perspective on learning through the SV.CO program by Rufaidul Mubarack</p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white border border-blue-200 rounded-lg p-4">
            <a href="https://medium.com/sv-co-blog/a-porcupine-in-the-nudist-colony-part-2-f8ce79ef691d" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-base font-semibold text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-700">A Porcupine in the Nudist colony - Part 2 (October 2017) ↗</a>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 mt-1">By Manoj Mohan, SV.CO English Language Coach</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <p class="text-xs text-slate-500 mt-4 italic">Note: More articles may be available at the Medium blog. Visit the links above to explore the full archive.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- 2016-2017: SV.CO Digital Transformation -->
      <div class="mb-12">
        <p class="text-xs font-bold tracking-wider uppercase text-slate-400 mb-2">2016-2017 - SV.CO Digital Transformation (External Media)</p>
        <div class="space-y-3">
          <div class="bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-lg p-4">
            <a href="https://yourstory.com/2016/07/startup-village" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-base font-semibold text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-700">YourStory - Startup Village Gets Makeover, Becomes World's First Digital Incubator ↗</a>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 mt-1">Leading startup media platform covering the digital transformation of Startup Village to SV.CO</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-lg p-4">
            <a href="https://thebetterindia.com/61810/startup-village-entrepreneurs-sv-co/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-base font-semibold text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-700">The Better India - World's First Digital Student Incubator to Reach 5 Million Students ↗</a>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 mt-1">In-depth feature on SV.CO's ambition to reach 5 million students in 3,500 engineering colleges</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-lg p-4">
            <a href="https://e27.co/worlds-first-digital-incubator-for-students-sv-co-aims-to-reach-all-pin-codes-in-india-20160725/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-base font-semibold text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-700">e27 - SV.CO Aims to Connect All of India to Silicon Valley ↗</a>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 mt-1">International startup media covering SV.CO's vision and Silicon Valley program</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-lg p-4">
            <a href="https://www.business-standard.com/article/pti-stories/digital-student-incubator-claimed-as-world-s-1st-goes-online-116071400413_1.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-base font-semibold text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-700">Business Standard - Digital Student Incubator Goes Online ↗</a>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 mt-1">National business daily coverage of SV.CO's launch</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-lg p-4">
            <a href="https://ssrana.in/articles/india-kochi-startup-village-launches-worlds-first-digital-incubator-for-students/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-base font-semibold text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-700">S.S. Rana & Co. - Kochi Startup Village Launches World's First Digital Incubator ↗</a>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 mt-1">Legal and IP perspective on the SV.CO launch and its significance</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-lg p-4">
            <a href="https://medium.com/sv-co-blog/scaling-startup-village-the-sv-co-story-b5d033ccbdd1" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-base font-semibold text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-700">Medium - Scaling Startup Village: The SV.CO Story! ↗</a>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 mt-1">First-hand account from the SV.CO team on Medium blog</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-lg p-4">
            <a href="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/city/kochi/sv-co-worlds-first-online-incubator-for-students-rolls-out-batch-with-32-teams/articleshow/56491170.cms" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-base font-semibold text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-700">Times of India - World's First Online Incubator for Students ↗</a>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 mt-1">Coverage of SV.CO's first cohort launch with 32 teams</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-lg p-4">
            <a href="https://sg.news.yahoo.com/world-first-digital-incubator-students-sv-co-aims-103723981.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-base font-semibold text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-700">Yahoo News Singapore - SV.CO Aims to Connect India to Silicon Valley ↗</a>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 mt-1">International coverage of SV.CO's global ambitions</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- 2018: Facebook Partnership -->
      <div class="mb-12">
        <p class="text-xs font-bold tracking-wider uppercase text-slate-400 mb-2">2018 - Facebook Partnership</p>
        <div class="space-y-3">
          <div class="bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-lg p-4">
            <a href="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/business/india-business/sv-co-facebook-to-partner-with-academia-for-tech-training/articleshow/62058516.cms" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-base font-semibold text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-700">Times of India - SV.CO & Facebook Partnership ↗</a>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 mt-1">Coverage of the Facebook VR School of Innovation partnership for tech training with universities</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- 2019: Pupilfirst Platform -->
      <div class="mb-12">
        <p class="text-xs font-bold tracking-wider uppercase text-slate-400 mb-2">2019-Present - Pupilfirst Platform</p>
        <div class="space-y-3">
          <div class="bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-lg p-4">
            <a href="https://www.pupilfirst.org/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-base font-semibold text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-700">Pupilfirst Official Site ↗</a>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 mt-1">Official website showcasing Pupilfirst's work in digital transformation of Indian classroom education</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-lg p-4">
            <a href="https://github.com/pupilfirst/pupilfirst" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-base font-semibold text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-700">Pupilfirst on GitHub (Open Source) ↗</a>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 mt-1">Open-source LMS codebase - learning through focused tasks, directed feedback, and community interaction</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-lg p-4">
            <a href="https://docs.pupilfirst.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-base font-semibold text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-700">Pupilfirst LMS Documentation ↗</a>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 mt-1">Complete technical documentation for platform features, setup, and deployment</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-lg p-4">
            <a href="https://rocket.pupilfirst.org/rocket" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-base font-semibold text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-700">Pupilfirst Rocket Platform (Live Demo) ↗</a>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 mt-1">Live reference implementation showing curriculum and cohort management features in action</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-lg p-4">
            <a href="https://www.pupilfirst.org/story" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-base font-semibold text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-700">Pupilfirst Story Page ↗</a>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 mt-1">The evolution from Startup Village to SV.CO to Pupilfirst told on their official site</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-lg p-4">
            <a href="https://www.pupilfirst.org/engineering" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-base font-semibold text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-700">Engineering at Pupilfirst ↗</a>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 mt-1">Technical blog and engineering insights from the Pupilfirst team</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-lg p-4">
            <a href="https://in.linkedin.com/showcase/pupilfirst-com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-base font-semibold text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-700">Pupilfirst on LinkedIn ↗</a>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 mt-1">Official LinkedIn page with updates and company information</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Related Organizations -->
      <div class="mb-12">
        <p class="text-xs font-bold tracking-wider uppercase text-slate-400 mb-2">Related Organizations & Resources</p>
        <div class="space-y-3">
          <div class="bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-lg p-4">
            <a href="https://makervillage.in/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-base font-semibold text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-700">Maker Village ↗</a>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 mt-1">India's largest electronics hardware incubator, part of the Startup Village ecosystem</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-lg p-4">
            <a href="https://keralastartupmission.wordpress.com/tag/startup-village/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-base font-semibold text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-700">Kerala Startup Mission - Startup Village Posts ↗</a>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 mt-1">Official blog posts and updates from Kerala Startup Mission about Startup Village</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Footer Navigation -->
      <div class="mt-16 pt-8 border-t border-slate-200 text-center">
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 mb-4">
          This archive is part of the EduMyna story documentation.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-4 text-sm">
          <a href="/story" class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-700">Read the Full Story →</a>
          <span class="text-slate-400">·</span>
          <a href="/founder-story" class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-700">About Gautam →</a>
          <span class="text-slate-400">·</span>
          <a href="/links" class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-700">All Resources →</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </Container>
</Layout>
